    "DataType enum has MIX='mix' in training (model.py) vs only IMAGE/VIDEO in base (diffusion/conditioner.py).",
    "VideoConditionerWithTraingOnlyEmb.get_condition_uncondition always forces FrameRepeatAttr dropout_rate=1.0 (always dropped during inference), enabling training-only frame repeat conditioning.",
    "DiffusionModel (model.py) broadcasts all data_batch tensors via _broadcast() across TP/CP groups before conditioning.",
    "ExtendDiffusionModel.get_data_and_condition calls add_condition_video_indicator_and_video_input_mask to inject VideoExtendCondition fields from the raw latent.",
    "Dataset_3D emits action tensor shape [T-1, 7] scaled by c_act_scaler=[20,20,20,20,20,20,1]; action is consumed by ActionConditionalGeneralDIT/TrajectoryAttr downstream.",
